Cursor undo :						cmd + U

Go up :								↑
Go down :							↓
Go left :							←
Go right :							→

Add Cursor up :						option + cmd + ↑
Add Cursor down :					option + cmd + ↓

Move Cursor BoL :					cmd + ←
Move Cursor EoL :					cmd + →

Select character :					maj + ↑ / ↓ / ← / →
Select word:						option + maj + ←→
Select line :						
Expand selection :					ctrl + maj + ←→
Select all occurrences :			maj + cmd + L
Select all :						cmd + A

Delete left part cursor :			cmd + backspace
Delete left word cursor :			option + backspace
Delete after cursor :				ctrl + D

Go to bracket :						maj + cmd + \
Go to last edit :					cmd K + cmd Q
Go to line :						ctrl + G